The municipal government of Garzeno is committed to preserving the town's cultural heritage, promoting sustainable development, and enhancing the quality of life for its inhabitants. The council works closely with regional and national authorities to secure funding and support for local initiatives, ranging from infrastructure projects to cultural events.

