Tourism is a growing sector in Garzeno, with visitors drawn to the municipality's scenic landscapes, historical sites, and cultural events. The town offers a range of accommodations, from charming bed and breakfasts to rustic agriturismi, providing visitors with an authentic experience of rural Italian life.

